{"tid":1215354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【做得幾多得幾多】5個聯署有4個倘未達標","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T17:08:45.000Z","uid":106205,"like":154,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d7abea7c86c735104f77dbe455c6258404a8a0","tid":1215354,"uid":106205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"有人整合咗，我幫手執一執<br />\n呢個時期大家做得幾多得幾多<br />\n唔理有無用，呢啲做多咗無壞🙌🏻<br />\n<br />\n1️⃣ 吊銷支持修訂《逃犯條例》中港官員簽證及美國國籍（7.4萬人簽署，差2.6萬人達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MGcgY8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MGcgY8&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=4c6bc5c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MGcgY8</a><br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ 與首個大至相同，但額外要求美國禁止所有支持修訂《逃犯條例》的香港立法會議員及其直系家屬入境。<br />\n<br />\n拒絕香港違反人權官員簽證入境（2,500人簽署，差9.75萬人達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2X9hZJS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2X9hZJS&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=43333ef5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2X9hZJS</a><br />\n<br />\n3️⃣ 以「要求制裁香港《逃犯條例》修訂案負責人」為題，要求美國吊銷所有相關官員的簽證，充公他們在美國境內的物業和財產，以及落實其他合法的制裁措施，至今已有三萬人響應。聯署表示，保障人權是美國外交政策的根基，促請華府根據《全球馬格尼斯基人權問責法》（The Global Magnitsky Human Rights Accountability Act），制裁相關人士。<br />\n<br />\n要求制裁香港《逃犯條例》修訂案負責人（3萬人簽署，差7萬人達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZilNG7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZilNG7&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=ed6ee6a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZilNG7</a><br />\n<br />\n4️⃣ 香港一旦修訂《逃犯條例》，中國可依據過去不確實的罪案，引渡入境香港的美國人到內地受審。聯署指出，在中美兩國爆發貿易戰、中國曾為政治利益「編造罪案」、綁架外國人的前提下，美國目前面臨的威脅已經十分明顯，不可接受，敦促華府盡快制裁所有支持修訂《逃犯條例》的香港政治人物。<br />\n制裁違反美國利益的香港官員（5,600人簽署，差9.44萬人達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZgQ1JE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZgQ1JE&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=cd1ef0ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZgQ1JE</a><br />\n<br />\n5️⃣ 南韓聯署 （附圖）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.president.go.kr/petitions/Temp/vVji3E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.president.go.kr%2Fpetitions%2FTemp%2FvVji3E&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=4d60dc2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.president.go.kr/petitions/Temp/vVji3E</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓嘅朋友好緊張我地香港嘅情況 我地去信咗青瓦台 只要聯署夠20萬 南韓政府就必須就今次事件作出回應<br />\n希望大家幫幫手 <br />\n雖然全部韓文 但個度得一個制禁 <br />\n禁完會叫你揀翻個social platform facebook / kakao /twitter/ naver <br />\n（中間藍色制，然後選擇帳戶身份登入就會成功聯署）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiEExZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiEExZn.png&h=0255c3ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d7f8c87c60f8280c068e64fd3ab3c0b4b8d9ab1","tid":1215354,"uid":106205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d515bfcaa71acc9348d0e9c1515d35ed51d1e8b1","tid":1215354,"uid":106205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:54:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4ee52e7b52b95a1b834a3ea907ec2b841486f8cf","tid":1215354,"uid":106205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:55:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"33cd1cc63b03a7961f95f20a7d05cd3cef7435fc","tid":1215354,"uid":106205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"af81a54d8eec2f27eb0a7f6d817e6d4910e59fad","tid":1215354,"uid":73509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:59:43.000Z","msg":"Signed and push!"},{"pid":"1f0aec4a497399c5f66e816d2f0f87a716a7994c","tid":1215354,"uid":106205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:59:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dcd532ba32828a7c614fd1764fe6764ae1bd568f","tid":1215354,"uid":106205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"盡可能share多啲俾人<br />\n就算佢哋唔出去都叫做有做啲嘢<br />\n係好絕望但係事實係咁"},{"pid":