%2Famp%2F&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=42deedc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/observer.com/2016/07/why-using-url-shorteners-may-expose-your-private-information/amp/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:03:24.000Z","msg":"唔好意思我唔知道咁會洩漏私隱<br />\n我係諗住整合一次過俾人聯署🙌🏻<br />\n如果有問題嘅話大家暫時唔好撳入去住"},{"pid":"8680a22b622e4db4f24cfca1115cdcd15e88dcac","tid":1215354,"uid":106205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69e4563b7c9775be6618ff016e318d8767b3b69f","tid":1215354,"uid":209337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:22:53.000Z","msg":"Like下個page ，我覺得爭取反送中，仲有好多可能性，好多勇士行最高，但係其實好多人都想係屋企默默付出！ <br />\n長期作戰，理性，非暴力！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Arrowofpeace/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FArrowofpeace%2F&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=4aeab0a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Arrowofpeace/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"Liked!"},{"pid":"581d2367d2c9ebf023744711458a32aa61856a5e","tid":1215354,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"faa8ec876b1ef0526c4c3c04027749f7300eee70","tid":1215354,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:33:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e2d87a4f365c8aabd414fd663239ad9e19c2c3b","tid":1215354,"uid":5136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f1d7abea7c86c735104f77dbe455c6258404a8a0","tid":1215354,"uid":106205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"有人整合咗，我幫手執一執<br />\n呢個時期大家做得幾多得幾多<br />\n唔理有無用，呢啲做多咗無壞🙌🏻<br />\n<br />\n1️⃣ 吊銷支持修訂《逃犯條例》中港官員簽證及美國國籍（7.4萬人簽署，差2.6萬人達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MGcgY8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MGcgY8&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=4c6bc5c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MGcgY8</a><br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ 與首個大至相同，但額外要求美國禁止所有支持修訂《逃犯條例》的香港立法會議員及其直系家屬入境。<br />\n<br />\n拒絕香港違反人權官員簽證入境（2,500人簽署，差9.75萬人達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2X9hZJS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2X9hZJS&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=43333ef5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2X9hZJS</a><br />\n<br />\n3️⃣ 以「要求制裁香港《逃犯條例》修訂案負責人」為題，要求美國吊銷所有相關官員的簽證，充公他們在美國境內的物業和財產，以及落實其他合法的制裁措施，至今已有三萬人響應。聯署表示，保障人權是美國外交政策的根基，促請華府根據《全球馬格尼斯基人權問責法》（The Global Magnitsky Human Rights Accountability Act），制裁相關人士。<br />\n<br />\n要求制裁香港《逃犯條例》修訂案負責人（3萬人簽署，差7萬人達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZilNG7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZilNG7&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=ed6ee6a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZilNG7</a><br />\n<br />\n4️⃣ 香港一旦修訂《逃犯條例》，中國可依據過去不確實的罪案，引渡入境香港的美國人到內地受審。聯署指出，在中美兩國爆發貿易戰、中國曾為政治利益「編造罪案」、綁架外國人的前提下，美國目前面臨的威脅已經十分明顯，不可接受，敦促華府盡快制裁所有支持修訂《逃犯條例》的香港政治人物。<br />\n制裁違反美國利益的香港官員（5,600人簽署，差9.44萬人達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZgQ1JE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZgQ1JE&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=cd1ef0ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZgQ1JE</a><br />\n<br />\n5️⃣ 南韓聯署 （附圖）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.president.go.kr/petitions/Temp/vVji3E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.president.go.kr%2Fpetitions%2FTemp%2FvVji3E&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=4d60dc2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.president.go.kr/petitions/Temp/vVji3E</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓嘅朋友好緊張我地香港嘅情況 我地去信咗青瓦台 只要聯署夠20萬 南韓政府就必須就今次事件作出回應<br />\n希望大家幫幫手 <br />\n雖然全部韓文 但個度得一個制禁 <br />\n禁完會叫你揀翻個social platform facebook / kakao /twitter/ naver <br />\n（中間藍色制，然後選擇帳戶身份登入就會成功聯署）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiEExZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiEExZn.png&h=0255c3ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"南韓聯署嘅中文翻譯 ig見到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> not perfect but用住先<br />\n<br />\n二零一九年六月九號，香港人響應反《逃犯條例》大遊行示威。若此法通過，香港司法部可將逃犯移交中國內地受審，此行為對人權侵犯極大。為反對逃犯條例修訂，多於一百萬香港市民參與六月九日遊行。<br />\n<br />\n然而香港政府漠視香港百萬市民意見，堅決於同月十二號舉行會議發表二讀。香港市民將行動升級，而香港警方更對香港市民使用武力，包括胡椒噴霧，催淚彈，催淚水，橡膠子彈及布袋彈，對市民造成嚴重傷害。香港正危在旦夕，現正請求各國，包括大韓民國，發出對香港旅行警報，並重新審視港韓外交條約。<br />\n<br />\n我們了解到大韓民國非常重視人權保護於移交的重要性。現正要求大韓民國政府帶頭對外宣揚此事，並於有需要時對香港採取行動，以協助香港民主穩定。"},{"pid":"299ab5640e936e1b30a387ec3217e4ef37324b8c","tid":1215354,"uid":61593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:56:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cf65617b6ea5c55411826c7821b5fc6f4af2f5cc","tid":1215354,"uid":61593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:57:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ad3789bff9ee2850668e1a8693761d7a63dd0157","tid":1215354,"uid":61593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:57:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0decc972374b44a4b498fec8cd54d979a7c452e7","tid":1215354,"uid":106205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"Don&rsquo;t stop pushing!"},{"pid":"6b3ea18da419b8e00dea5af2e63408effb9ffd6d","tid":1215354,"uid":106205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3caf763a11b07c05d0ef59e862f84b230e93542","tid":1215354,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:03:40.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"3b8ddfe0ca881e48175d4a426b9c190281b69885","tid":1215354,"uid":81693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:04:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a633ec105ccc96bc71ce8b3a0f437b26259f2f3f","tid":1215354,"uid":63808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:06:12.000Z","msg":"佢地得3萬人，呢幾日要做良